money. I wish there was money everywhere all the time easy to get. There are a lot of jobs available but is the pay good. I will work in McDonalds for a month then leave because of the pay. I get paid as little as $5 a week. Its rubbish. Sometime though you have to work like that to save up money to better your condition. I’m hoping that maybe one day Zimbabwe can produce so much gold that it can sell to other countries in the world and become a rich country rich with new ideas though, gold alone cannot help anybody. I guess it depends also on the government. Hmm, I’ll keep my hopes high for myself, my country and the world.

Carmen x
